[[File:GepsGrill-GG7.jpg|thumb|250px|A [[Whiphid/Legends|Whiphid]] vendor sells [[Bantha burger/Legends|bantha burgers]] and [[Dewback/Legends|dewback]] [[Rib/Legends|ribs]]]]
'''Dewback ribs''' were the grilled [[Rib/Legends|haunch]] of a [[Dewback/Legends|dewback]].

They were sold by the [[Whiphid/Legends|Whiphids]] [[Fillin Ta]] and [[Norun Gep]], at [[Gep's Grill]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The meat was bought from hunters on the outskirts of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], and occasionally needed to have the former owner's brand removed before it could be sold. On slow weeks, the Whiphid partners would loot the [[Bantha/Legends|bantha]] stalls to supplement their supplies.

Dewback ribs were popular with the local workers.

